title: PAWNSHOP / KIM GLASS barks
description: Kim reacts to you clicking on the glass.

dialogueTree.title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Not top-of-the-line glass. Hope he..."
dialogueTree.english: "Not top-of-the-line glass. Hope he never has to rely on it."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie jest to szkło z najwyższej półki. Oby nigdy nie musiał na nim polegać”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Гэта не шкло найвышэйшай якасці. Спадзяюся, яму ніколі не давядзецца на яго спадзявацца".
